qas.question: On what date in 2011 was the hold on Schwarzenegger's movie projects announced?
2013's The Last Stand marked Schwarzenegger's first starring role in how long?
What was the first film Schwarzenegger co-starred in with Sylvester Stallone?
What's the title of the fifth film in the Terminator franchise?
What year did Terminator Genisys debut?

context: On <a0_0>May 20<a0_0/>, 2011, Schwarzenegger's entertainment counsel announced that all movie projects currently in development were being halted: "Schwarzenegger is focusing on personal matters and is not willing to commit to any production schedules or timelines". On July 11, 2011, it was announced that Schwarzenegger was considering a comeback film despite his legal problems. He appeared in The Expendables 2 (2012), and starred in The Last Stand (2013), his first leading role in <a1_0>10 years<a1_0/>, and <a2_0>Escape Plan<a2_0/> (2013), his first co-starring role alongside Sylvester Stallone. He starred in Sabotage, released in March 2014, and appeared in The Expendables 3, released in August 2014. He starred in the fifth Terminator movie <a3_0>Terminator Genisys<a3_0/> in <a4_0>2015<a4_0/> and will reprise his role as Conan the Barbarian in The Legend of Conan.
